HEADWORD: Functionally
<hw>Func"tion*al*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a functional manner;
as regards normal or appropriate activity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The organ is said to be <qex>functionally</qex> disordered.</q>
<rj><qau>Lawrence.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

